Package com.iciql.util

Utility classes for iciql.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IciqlLogger.IciqlListener Interface that defines an iciql listener.
 

Class Summary
GenerateModels Generates iciql models.
IciqlLogger Utility class to optionally log generated statements to IciqlListeners.
Statement logging is disabled by default.
JdbcUtils This is a utility class with JDBC helper functions.
Slf4jIciqlListener Slf4jIciqlListener interfaces the IciqlLogger to the SLF4J logging framework.
StatementBuilder A utility class to build a statement.
StringUtils Common string utilities.
Utils Generic utility methods.
WeakIdentityHashMap<K,V> This hash map uses weak references, so that elements that are no longer referenced elsewhere can be garbage collected.
 

Enum Summary
IciqlLogger.StatementType Enumeration of the different statement types that are logged.
Slf4jIciqlListener.Level Enumeration representing the SLF4J log levels.
